AutoCensoR CPU Only

This package contains the Windows CPU-only desktop runtime for AutoCensoR.
Model weights, private datasets, personal paths, account links, API keys,
telemetry, and cloud-upload code are not included.

Korean and English UI text is stored as UTF-8. The app uses operating-system
font fallbacks for the interface. Some bundled third-party packages may include
their own fonts or license files for their internal runtime needs.

Runtime dependencies are bundled under the application `_internal` directory.
Those dependencies are not relicensed by this project. Review the included
package metadata and license files before redistributing this package.
